    "Moreover, Fig. 6 presents false detection on a mammographic image from the INbreast dataset.",
    "At the same time, Fig. 7 illustrates detection results on some images on FFDM vs. its corresponding CESM images from the CDD-CESM dataset.",
    "Tables 6 and 7 show that the performance of YOLO is better at detecting the existence of masses regardless its type.",
    "Also, Tables 7 and 8 show that the higher input image size improves the detection accuracy as the best mAP is achieved at input size of 640.",
    "The 640-input size achieved mAP of 98.96% in INbreast dataset, 81.52% on CESM images and 71.65% on DM images from CDD_CESM dataset."
